Hi all! The crafting key that I added yesterday is working for me!
Are other folks still having problems? It had stopped working at one point, but maybe raising the limits fixed things?

the issue is that Jordy and Nikolaos need a key on their local envs to run ibllm benchmarks, not their crafting env

i guess we can see if other people see problems in crafting envs? i haven't heard of any so far
Ah, that is a special case -- if you need to override the open AI api key for a reason like this, then placing the special key in `env-local-overrides.yaml` is the way to go.
Otherwise, most folks should use the default auto-provisioned key in Crafting!
